<h3>Paragogical Action Review</h3>

<ol>
<li>Review what was supposed to happen.<br><br></li>
<li>Establish what is happening/happened.<br><br></li>
<li>Determine what's right and wrong with what we're doing.<br><br></li>
<li>What did we learn or change?<br><br></li>
<li>What else should we change going forward?<br><br></li>
</ol>

